				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Anyone boxing a Bard and Cleric?<a name="69889"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Nov 17 04 3:48 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span> I'm thinking of starting a new account and making a Cleric to occasionally play with my Bard. I am wondering if its worth it. I would mainly use it for healing me while I chant kited named  mobs that summon and hit very hard or are non-mezzable. In some situations I would be straight up meleeing.
<br />

<br />
 My question for anyone who does this is, is it possible to keep agro off the Cleric when he heals you? In the case of chant kiting it seems unlikely since the agro nerf. Even in the case of meleeing it would seem unlikely. I could get a BoC but if I need a heal before it proc's then its not going to be any help.
<br />

<br />
 I am also looking for a guide to 2 boxing on one computer.</span></td>
