				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Anyone boxing a Bard and Cleric?<a name="69985"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Nov 19 04 12:49 AM</span></td>
