				<td colspan="2"><span>I box a 70 shaman or a 70 cleric with my bard. In my case Cleric &gt; Shaman. While the shaman adds buffs and can do some dps with dots there simply is no beating the cleric HoT heals. You can even nuke with the cleric if you get really bored<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
Cast Holy Elixer on pull, hos and slow. Crank up the DS and just melee them down. When they start to run root them with the cleric or go rogue on them while snared though root + DS is faster.</span></td>
